Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:30.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:36.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:44.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:51.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:01:00.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:05.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:10.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:15.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:22.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉得了『灼热病』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚跑去请求尼莫帮助玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却遭到拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚逼问他说 是杀人重要 还是救人重要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来娜蒂亚也不幸染病
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两人徘徊在生死边缘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到救了他们两人的 竟然就是尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.99,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#15 鹦鹉螺号的最大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森 启动开关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是引擎用的 耐热硬化玻陨石板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样的高温也不会熔化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,利用这种板子的特性 以及这艘船的强大电力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然在短短三天 就能发明出金属切割器…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们真是天才\N我们真是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那也是因为有这艘船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进行得如何？强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还顺利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 多亏有你送的耐热板 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多出来的耐热板碎片 没想到也能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这艘船的技术 真的好了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点 不然鹦鹉螺号要穿孔了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好险赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼镜不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦？你们在吵什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这副眼镜是我长大之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸买给我的 唯一一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为他几乎都不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有形的东西迟早会坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是命中注定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是神要我 别为了爸爸的事想不开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,东西坏了修好就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除了人命之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大多数的东西 都是有办法补救的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,覆水虽然难收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是再加满就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我看看 我来把它修好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里有办法修眼镜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船就算无法靠岸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大部分的事情 也都能在船内处理好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 这是科学的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以那么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两点钟方向发现不明航行物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深度浅 速度也慢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会是鲸鱼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这家伙也有可能是 长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以目前的距离无法判断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先接近再说\N了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经修好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的耶 就跟原来的一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你 菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 这是科学的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你跟娜蒂亚 进展得不顺利是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就把这个拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有女生收到花会不开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 这些花是怎么来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是在这艘船上制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也算是科学的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好干喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 这艘船实在太便利了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算便利又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这只会让人们愈来愈懒惰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人们会愈来愈幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来 这送你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些花是怎么来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是他们在这艘船上 制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么便利又科学的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它终究不过是个杀人工具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然由人类来创造花草树木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那样跟石像鬼又有什么不同？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号 1888年6月21日下水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒 这是鹦鹉螺号的记录板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 下头的文字板写了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱顿琉姆 恒星历7962年进入宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看得懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 你竟然看得懂这种字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到你还有这种才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我看得懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这些字是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎室的记录板？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 就是写了鹦鹉螺号 下水日期的那块板子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 你看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那下方的文字板 是什么材质？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既非金属又不是石材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且还用奇怪的文字写了 『爱顿琉姆』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你看得懂那种文字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是 是娜蒂亚念出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 是娜蒂亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类的优点就是 会想去知道自己不明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好奇心与求知欲是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个世界上 有些事情还是不知道的好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 有时一无所知 反而会比较幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接近中的航行物 确认为长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰就战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰就战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备对潜水舰战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就战斗位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又要打仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 我们到舰桥去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是不是说战斗中不能进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们只是稍微看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要你看过鹦鹉螺号 打败长嘴硬鳞鱼号的威风模样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定会喜欢上这艘船的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号有动静吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有变化 距离5000
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么对方没有发射鱼雷攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道是放弃抵抗了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为鹦鹉螺号的防御系统 无懈可击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除非大型战舰联合攻击过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然是伤不了这艘船的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们怎么可以进来 目前正在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我想看看 这艘船的威风模样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里不是小孩子的游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,碰到某种东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是陷阱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是对方的新武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超电磁推进器的磁场 遭到扰乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,探测系统的电源受损
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火器管制装置断线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无法航行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷鱼雷接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鱼雷4枚 目测距离4000
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拦截防卫装置？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无法启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诱导至最接近位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于距离800时 将所有水槽注水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进行急速下降
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离1200
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离800
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有水槽注水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过来了 还有300
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,3枚分别由上下通过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,较迟的第4枚要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,通过舰桥前方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,推测应该是在九点钟方向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发现长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正由左舷接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全速直驶而来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它打算冲撞过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,行不通 船身完全动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷船员回避至右舷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰准备接受撞击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 把它弹回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是个乱来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是上头命令它 与鹦鹉螺号同归于尽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太残忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船舰受损情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷第7水槽破损
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,探测装置无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷已停止漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎全部无法运转
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除了浮出海面 从舰外进行修复之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全部水槽排水 浮出海面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶的海中怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰炮击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰炮击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标 左舷的大型潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要替亚伯拉罕号报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用这艘2号舰 梭鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及美国联合舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明已经打败 长嘴硬鳞鱼号了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷前方发现美国舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,初弹命中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干的好 第二齐射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射 发射 尽量发射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沉下去吧 可恶的海中怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确认发炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二波要过来了 还有50秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰耐爆防御
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,封闭所有装甲门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,急速潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有办法 潜航装置无法启动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样啊 副船长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸好我们相信了 那个男人说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是指那个戴着面具的男人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,戴着面具的人是谁都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要能为那些海上男儿报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射！发射！发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为强与娜蒂亚报仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷舰尾中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,二号辅助引擎受损
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰首潜舵直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将1号至32号的压缩空气 全部抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是那么一来 船舰的浮力将…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开启所有安全气阀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别让它溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射 发射 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,击中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标沉没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深度150公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷多处进水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷排水帮浦 全速运转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,着陆 水深200公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放出3号至6号的重油 以及后部机库的资材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,假装已遭歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,资材及重油释放完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各部门着手紧急维修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下子我们所剩的力量 只足够再浮出海面一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在只能静候 上方舰队受骗离去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰长 没想到这么简单就解决掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 还不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先观察一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对方毕竟是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长度达150公尺的实用潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟会是哪一国的船呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是哪一国都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它可是数千名海上男儿的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,击沉它是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这已经没办法修了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辅助第二引擎舱 发生有毒原子气体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将辅助引擎舱完全封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是菲特及另外两名人员 还在里头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进行封锁\N尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 找不到舱口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轮机长 拜托你 请你打开这道闸门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不快的话 菲特会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在开启的话 你们也会遭到危险物质感染
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不能让你们继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船不是以几百年后的 科学技术制造出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是艘什么都办得到的船吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你救救菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船确实是超科学的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但并不是万能的天神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也有无能为力的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要就这样见死不救！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有其它办法了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要浮出海面排除气体 或许他们会有救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但现在情况不允许我们那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是现在浮出海面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船就会成为战舰的弹靶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你在那边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我马上就会救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是跑来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连你也会一起送命的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要…我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长的判断是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是闸门的封锁再迟一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,气体就会蔓延至整个引擎舱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,牺牲是愈少愈好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是我的命运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长 请你浮出海面 救救菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么不浮上去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船的秘密 真有那么重要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要浮出海面竖起白旗 战舰就不会再攻击过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都会得救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么又要杀人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次是你的同伴耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你根本就不是人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不准你再说下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为最痛苦的人是尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船的科学 还不是人类所能驾驭的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以绝对不能展现在世人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要明白这点 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有请你不要责备尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因为有他在 我才会搭上这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长 请你务必要完成 船上众人的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,消灭新亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 多保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要跟娜蒂亚好好相处喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要有我的花 一定能够成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还不想死！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还有好多事没去做！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还…\N菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲特…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妨碍物质消磁完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.06,0:22:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各探测装置恢复正常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海上及海中皆未发现舰影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美国舰队似乎已经撤离了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 浮出海面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲特 这是你的花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.05,0:23:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这群人实在太冷血了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己的同伴死了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连替他哀悼的时间都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船正在与 新亚特兰提斯作战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正在互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.88,0:23:54.65,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.72,0:24:02.79,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:07.79,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.87,0:24:12.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.24,0:24:21.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.21,0:24:31.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.32,0:24:40.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.17,0:24:44.26,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.34,0:24:48.97,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.04,0:24:58.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.76,0:25:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我想请你帮我调查蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.13,0:25:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水的材质究竟是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.67,0:25:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.03,0:25:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头有好多细致的纹路
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且还是立体的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.11,0:25:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.74,0:25:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因为有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.41,0:25:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才会发生恐怖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.05,0:25:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『消失大陆的秘密』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.28,0:25:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔\N要看喔
